version_description:
- Customize Kickerinho! Pick from over 100 jerseys and 25 balls!
- Unlock new tricks: Heel Stall, Sit Down, Around The World
- Gain experience, level up and get collectible cards!
- Some minor enhancements: screenshot sharing, balance indicator, new In-App menu

* 6 French jerseys
* 2 new leaderboards
* optimizations and bugfixes

* 20 new levels!
* 9 new tricks!
* 4 new achievements!
* level up faster with the new experience mixture!
* free gifts!

Meet 7 new characters that came to Rio to celebrate Halloween:

• Vladinho
• Skeletinho
• Muminho
• Clownhio
• Frankinhio
• Zombinho
• Diablinho

Each comes with it's own mood and frenzy effects!

* Reduced build size
* Improved loading times
* Improved performance
- fixed a problem with Game Center achievements on iOS9

This time we did some bug fixes and optimizations so that you have the best possible experience.

If you like this game please consider leaving a comment! If you have any questions writes us at contact@orbitalknight.com or send a message on Facebook.

Kickerinho fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/kickerinho/
OrbitalKnight fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/OrbitalKnightCrew/

Thanks!
